---+ changelog for import-20070116 (previous import-20061124)
   * .ltibrc
      * add option to bypass proxy testing

   * ltib
      * Add a hint for debugging LWP (network connection tests)
      * Remove x/y/{a,b,c} constructs (for the dash shell on ubuntu-edgy)
      * Make MD5 sum tests apply even if the file is already local

   * bin/Ltibutils.pm
      * Aocally reset SIG{__DIE__} so we don't obscure LWP::UserAgent messages
      during proxy tests
      * Respect the .ltibrc option bypass_network_tests to disable network
      tests (for misbehaving proxies)
      * Add a check to see if the http_proxy has not been set if asking
      for proxies and complain and then ignore.
      * Improve proxy test error handling (report status_line from
      $ua->request if it is not successful.
      * Don't test gpp/ppp if their respective resources in .ltibrc are not set
      * Add 10% pad size to created ramdisks so people can add stuff to their
      running system.
      * Add DEPLOYMENT_SREC (only appies to some platforms)

   * bin/autobuild_ltib
      * Add callout to mk_pkg_build_list, which is a new script that will
      give a full listing of the packages built by the autobuilder (not
      just the deltas)

   * bin/device_genromfs.txt
      * Update dsp,c,x,x

   * bin/listpkginfo
      * Add toolchain srpms to the output list

   * bin/mk_pkg_build_list
      * New script, it builts a list of all packages built/failed by the
      autobuilder by parsing the build.log file

   * config/defaults/busybox.config
      * Add CONFIG_LFS, CONFIG_SEQ

   * config/platform/mpc8360epb/defconfig
